OL,3,CTrial of Nottingham Forest owner's
OL,4,Clibel claim against rival to be held
OL,5,Cin 2027
OL,7,FThe trial of Nottingham Forest owner
OL,8,FEvangelos Marinakis's High Court libel
OL,9,Fclaim against a Greek football rival
OL,10,Fis set to be held in 2027.
OL,12,FMr Marinakis, who also owns Greek side
OL,13,FOlympiacos, is suing Eirini Karypidou,
OL,14,Fthe chairman of Greek Super League
OL,15,Frivals Aris, over several "false"
OL,16,Fallegations, including that he had
OL,17,Fconducted match-fixing and was
OL,18,Finvolved in a high-profile drug
OL,19,Ftrafficking case in the country, which
OL,20,Fhe denies.
OL,26,@wD@[OUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
