PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779383153
OL,3,CTrial of Nottingham Forest owner's
OL,4,Clibel claim against rival to be held
OL,5,Cin 2027
OL,7,FHe is also suing Israeli political
OL,8,Fconsultant Ari Harow and his company,
OL,9,FSheyaan Consulting Limited, whom Mr
OL,10,FMarinakis's lawyers claim were
OL,11,Finvolved in the "creation and
OL,12,Fimplementation" of the "smear"
OL,13,Fcampaign.
OL,15,FMs Karypidou, Mr Harow and Sheyaan
OL,16,FConsulting are defending the claim.
OL,26,@sD@QOUtD@OO]tD@XOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
