PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779383153
OL,3,CTrial of Nottingham Forest owner's
OL,4,Clibel claim against rival to be held
OL,5,Cin 2027
OL,7,FThe judge said that Mr Marinakis is
OL,8,Fseeking between #1 million and #5
OL,9,Fmillion in damages and claims the
OL,10,Fallegations against him had "caused
OL,11,Fhim serious reputational harm."
OL,13,FMr Justice Johnson said in his ruling
OL,14,Fthat Mr Marinakis is suing over
OL,15,Fallegations made on a website, social
OL,16,Fmedia and mobile billboards between
OL,17,FNovember 2023 and March 2024, which he
OL,18,Fdenies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779383153
OL,3,CTrial of Nottingham Forest owner's
OL,4,Clibel claim against rival to be held
OL,5,Cin 2027
OL,7,FThey included three articles published
OL,8,Fon a website called
OL,9,F"nottinghamforestfire.co.uk" in
OL,10,FNovember 2023.
OL,12,FSeveral posts were also published on X
OL,13,Fin December 2023, and six YouTube
OL,14,Fvideos uploaded, including two titled
OL,15,F"Marinakis Match Fixer" and "Marinakis
OL,16,FDrug Smuggler".
OL,18,FThe YouTube channel, X account and
OL,19,Fwebsite were all later taken down.
OL,26,@qD@\O]wD@AOUwD@WO]wD@]OUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779383153
OL,3,CTrial of Nottingham Forest owner's
OL,4,Clibel claim against rival to be held
OL,5,Cin 2027
OL,7,FThe allegations were also displayed on
OL,8,Fmobile billboards driven around
OL,9,FNottingham Forest's stadium, the City
OL,10,FGround, on two match days.
OL,12,FIn written submissions for a hearing
OL,13,Flast year, David Sherborne, for Mr
OL,14,FMarinakis, said the "highly
OL,15,Fdefamatory" allegations were
OL,16,F"completely untrue".
OL,26,@vD@UOUwD@KO]xD@AOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779383153
OL,3,CTrial of Nottingham Forest owner's
OL,4,Clibel claim against rival to be held
OL,5,Cin 2027
OL,7,FHe said they included that Mr
OL,8,FMarinakis was a "leader of a criminal
OL,9,Forganisation" and "guilty of match-
OL,10,Ffixing practices including extortion,
OL,11,Ffraud and arson", among others.
OL,13,FMatthew Hodson, for Ms Karypidou, told
OL,14,Fthe earlier hearing the social media
OL,15,Fcampaign had "limited publication" and
OL,16,F"fared pathetically", and that there
OL,17,Fwas no evidence of "actual harm" to Mr
OL,18,FMarinakis's reputation.
OL,20,FA further hearing in the claim could
OL,21,Ftake place later this year.
